                                        xtRecursive'.
--no-module-unknown-context-recursive   Negative
                                        'module-unknown-context-recursive'
                                        option.
--module-unknown-context-reg-exp [value]  Sets the regular expression when using
                                        the require function in a not
                                        statically analyse-able way.
